General.Name: Yandal Resources Ltd
General.Description: Yandal Resources Limited engages in the discovery, exploration, and development of gold properties. It holds 100% interests in the Ironstone Well and Barwidgee gold projects covering 470 square kilometer of Greenstone Belt; Mt McClure gold; White Dam; and Gordons gold projects in Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Orex Mining Pty Ltd and changed its name to Yandal Resources Limited in March 2018. Yandal Resources Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Nedlands, Australia.
